{"tid":1795053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"土耳其維族難民 憂隨時會被強送中國","createTime":"2019-12-23T14:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T20:52:52.000Z","uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e433795008bc0d529607e45254cde9760b14964c","tid":1795053,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"中共不斷打壓維吾爾族人，有逃離新疆、以難民身份到土耳其定居的維族人，近日卻擔心會遭當局驅逐出境、遣返中國，擔心他在土耳其建立的生活會消失。<br />\n六年前中共打壓維族人，Ablet Abdugani與家人以難民身份從中國逃到土耳其，他之後與其他流亡的維族人一同生活，並且與兄弟在首都伊斯坦堡外圍一同創立繙譯、出版的生意，他的妻子則在維族學校擔任教師，子女則在維族學校讀書，並且有機會回復他們原因的生活方式。<br />\nAbdugani的一家在土耳其生活看似美滿，不過與1.1萬流亡當地的維族一樣，擔心隨時會被當局驅逐出境，他說，他與其他40名維族商人都接到當局通知，要求他們離開土耳其，雖然當局未有強制將他們驅逐，但他表示在土耳其生活，一直都令他感到十分憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191223/60407974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F60407974&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlptAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=186828f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F60407974&h=9cde4e70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191223/60407974</a>"},{"pid":"198476b282c712ec036e52f6d394bbbdedde4662","tid":1795053,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"去台灣？"},{"pid":"354b2d4e4e51224586040b6290b121796763ff74","tid":1795053,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"198476b282c712ec036e52f6d394bbbdedde4662","tid":1795053,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"去台灣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"Agreed :("},{"pid":"fa9759c69711a70c33a09684abeecc859c01b32c","tid":1795053,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"198476b282c712ec036e52f6d394bbbdedde4662","tid":1795053,"uid":21545,"like":